VALUES
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00247', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '在一個探討「懷孕期間藥物使用」對「低出生體重危害」的病例對照研究中，發現偽陽性的 藥物使用報告在低出生體重兒童的母親中比正常出生體重兒童的母親中更常見，這屬於那一種 研究誤差：', '["選樣偏差（selectionbias）", "差別性分類錯誤（differentialmisclassification）", "無差別性分類錯誤（nondifferentialmisclassification）", "偵測錯誤（detectionbias）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8bdb1f273030", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cb646a1d0b7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00248', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '承上題，上述偏差最有可能導致所估計的勝算比（oddsratio）較真實值：', '["增加", "減少", "保持不變", "會改變，但方向無法預測"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8bdb1f273030", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cb646a1d0b7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00249', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '某學者建立一世代研究，欲探討吸菸和高血壓對心臟病風險的交互作用。研究結果發現，患有 高血壓的樣本中，有吸菸者和無吸菸者罹患心臟病之相差危險性為7×10-3、相對危險性為4.5， 而在非高血壓者中，有吸菸者和無吸菸者罹患心臟病之相差危險性為4×10-3、相對危險性為5。 試問此為下列何種交互作用？', '["加成性協同作用", "累乘性協同作用", "累乘性獨立作用", "加成性拮抗作用"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8bdb1f273030", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cb646a1d0b7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00250', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '已知甲暴露會降低乙疾病發生的風險，若某一干擾因子和甲暴露呈正相關，和乙疾病呈負相 關，未控制此干擾因子會對甲暴露和乙疾病的相關性產生何種影響？', '["導致趨零偏差（towardthenull）", "導致離零偏差（awayfromthenull）", "會讓甲暴露看起來的好處降低（lessbeneficial）", "有影響，但影響的方向性無法確認"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8bdb1f273030", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cb646a1d0b7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00251', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '一個探討生活滿意度和死亡率研究發現，「生活不滿意」和全死因死亡率呈劑量－反應關係 （dose-responserelationship）；控制年齡和社經地位後，相關性則減弱。此段敘述暗示：', '["年齡和社經地位為干擾因子，導致趨零偏差（towardthenull）", "年齡和社經地位為干擾因子，導致離零偏差（awayfromthenull）", "年齡和社經地位為干擾因子，導致精確度（precision）下降", "年齡和社經地位為修飾因子（modifier）"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8bdb1f273030", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cb646a1d0b7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 29, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00252', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '在控制干擾因子的方法中，下列何種方法最可能影響研究的外部效度？', '["隨機分配", "配對", "分層分析", "限制"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8bdb1f273030", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cb646a1d0b7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 30, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00253', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '某所學校有5,000名學生，麻疹疫苗的接種率為90%，但仍發生了一波麻疹疫情，共600名 學生感染，而感染者270人曾接種過麻疹疫苗，疫苗在此學校的效果約為下列何者？', '["95%", "91%", "87%", "84%"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8bdb1f273030", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cb646a1d0b7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 31, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00254', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於基礎再生數（basicreproductivenumber）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["是指在一個完全易感的群體中且沒有任何防疫措施的情況下，一個感染到某種傳染病的初 發個案，會把疾病傳染給其他多少個人的平均數", "天花基礎再生數約為4，因此要達到群體免疫所需的疫苗接種率至少為75%", "承上，一個天花的初發個案在1個世代（generation）後會感染4個人，2個世代後會有16 個人被感染，3個世代後會有64個人被感染", "基礎再生數是評估傳染病病原傳播力的指標，如果資料收集的夠完整且估算的方法正確， 則同一病原在不同地區所估算出的基礎再生數的值應該很接近"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8bdb1f273030", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cb646a1d0b7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 32, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00255', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '使用統合分析（meta-analysis），將 4 篇不同研究的結果合併成單一個綜合效果（summary effect），下列何者是最好的理由？', '["4篇研究均為高品質的研究", "異質性（heterogeneity）的統計檢定沒有偵測到異質性", "使用漏斗圖未發現出版偏差（publicationbias）", "研究問題、納入的族群、介入措施、追蹤方式和結果等都非常類似"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8bdb1f273030", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cb646a1d0b7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 33, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-00256', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-aaf759af', 'sub-public-health-specialist-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '評估篩檢計畫的實施過程中，由於某疾病在疾病自然史中有較長的臨床前期，導致篩檢計畫 看似有效的找出罹病個體，並使其接受臨床治療而有較佳的預後；然而真實情況則不然。此 即所謂以下何種偏差？', '["先導期偏差（leadtimebias）", "時距偏差（lengthbias）", "過度診斷偏差（overdiagnosisbias）", "自願者偏差"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:36+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "8bdb1f273030", "answer_pdf_sha1": "cb646a1d0b7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0803", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "流行病學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 34, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
